<varlistentry id="options.MyBackground">
	<term>MyBackground <emphasis remap='I'>"background_name"</emphasis></term>
	<listitem>
		<para>Specifies a background definition. Please note that only desktops can have different backgrounds
		- the viewports inside of a desktop are limited to the same background.</para>
		<para>See Also: <ulink url="MyBackground#synopsis">MyBackground definition</ulink> for further details.</para>
	</listitem>
</varlistentry>
